Data
  Data is the raw facts that can be processed for further modification.
  Example:We have a Data like Raj,orange and 12.

Information
   Processed data is an information.

Example:We have a Data called Raj but while we entering in a database or a table it can be mentioned as somename name is Raj.
Name->Raj
Likewise,we have orange it can be a fruit or a color according to the table.
12 can be a roll number,birth date or some pocket money.

DBMS-Data Base Management System
DBMS is used to store,insert,update,retrive and manage the data that is stored.
->It has interrelated data
->It can be of any Size.
Example
  DBMS can be used in Banks,education systems like Schools and colleges and Airlines.

